Text: Sattori, do you have an e-mail address?

Hi beldrog,
Though I have an email address, I don't share it with strangers. What do you want to know? Just ask here and I will see if I can answer.
Maybe you should get an e-mail address that you *can* share with strangers.
I am too lazy for this.
Maybe if you got an address you could share, someone would share something with you in return.
